================================================================================
to compile run the following
  `gcc main.c -o main`

p-machine offers two modes. regular mode, and interactive mode.
afterwards, run the `main` executable using this command
  ./main <yourfile>

to run in interactive mode, use this command
  ./main -i

================================================================================
